display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {Z} /\mathord {\sim }]]></fr:tex> is often denoted <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {Z} / n\mathbb {Z}]]></fr:tex>. Moreover, there are well-defined operations <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[[a]+[b]=[a+b]]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[[a]\cdot [b]=[a\cdot  b]]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter><fr:tree
