display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex> which are coprime to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>,
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\varphi (n)=|\{k\in \mathbb {N}\mid  k<n,\gcd (k,n)=1\}|.]]></fr:tex>
So <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\varphi (12)=|\{1,5,7,11\}|=4]]></fr:tex>, but <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\varphi (11)=10]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
